Body: Hi there i've created some ogg (oga) files to listen to on my HTC Desire.I've used very low bitrate settings.My HTC Desire music app does recognize the files an I can play but the playback skipps after a couple of seconds and jumps to the next track.Is there a low bitrate limitation for Ogg Vorbis files? A min. bitrate required?Link: supported media formats
